  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Retrospective analysis on colonoscopies in the endoscopy unit of the Lyell McEwin Hospital.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Colonoscopy reports will be manually searched by the investigator to evaluate epidemiology on
      colorectal lesions.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
